{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">知道平衡移动原理在沉淀溶解中的应用。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>+2NH<sub>4</sub>Cl=MgCl<sub>2</sub>+2NH<sub>3</sub>&uarr;+2H<sub>2</sub>O</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub>+2HCl=MgCl<sub>2</sub>+2H<sub>2</sub>O</span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：胶头滴管、试管、药匙；</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：氢氧化镁、蒸馏水、盐酸、氯化钠溶液。</span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在三支试管中分别加入少量氢氧化镁沉淀，然后分别滴加蒸馏水、盐酸和氯化铵溶液，观察实验现象。</span></span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">滴加蒸馏水的试管无明显现象，滴加盐酸和氯化铵溶液的试管中沉淀逐渐溶解。</span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}